CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780560334
OL,3,CFirst ovarian cancer treatment in two
OL,4,Cdecades approved for NHS use
OL,6,FHundreds of women with ovarian cancer
OL,7,Fare set to benefit after the first new
OL,8,Ftreatment for the hard-to-treat
OL,9,Fdisease in two decades was approved
OL,10,Ffor use in the NHS.
OL,12,FA significant proportion of women with
OL,13,Fovarian cancer are not diagnosed until
OL,14,Fthe disease is at a later stage,
OL,15,Fmeaning it is much harder to treat.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/8
