PN,30502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780560334
OL,3,CFirst ovarian cancer treatment in two
OL,4,Cdecades approved for NHS use
OL,6,FWomen with a certain form of late-
OL,7,Fstage disease, which has stopped
OL,8,Fresponding to chemotherapy, previously
OL,9,Fhad "limited" options, experts said as
OL,10,Fthey hailed the "landmark" decision
OL,11,Ffrom the National Institute for Health
OL,12,Fand Care Excellence (Nice).
OL,14,FFinal draft guidance from Nice says
OL,15,Fthat mirvetuximab soravtansine can be
OL,16,Fused for women with certain forms of
OL,17,Fovarian, fallopian tube or peritoneal
OL,18,Fcancers.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780560334
OL,3,CFirst ovarian cancer treatment in two
OL,4,Cdecades approved for NHS use
OL,6,FNice said that until recently, there
OL,7,Fhave been limited options for treating
OL,8,Fthese types of cancers when they stop
OL,9,Fresponding to traditional chemotherapy.
OL,11,FVictoria Clare, chief executive
OL,12,Fofficer of the charity Ovacome, said:
OL,13,F"Today marks a landmark moment. Being
OL,14,Ftold that platinum-based chemotherapy
OL,15,Fis no longer working can bring anxiety
OL,16,Fand uncertainty, particularly when the
OL,17,Fdisease is at an advanced stage, where
OL,18,Ftime and options are limited."
OL,20,FHow does it work?
OL,26,@uD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
