PN,30504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780560334
OL,3,CFirst ovarian cancer treatment in two
OL,4,Cdecades approved for NHS use
OL,6,FThe new treatment, also called Elahere
OL,7,Fand developed by AbbVie, is a targeted
OL,8,Ftherapy that works by attaching to
OL,9,Fcancer cells and destroying them, with
OL,10,Fsuch treatments sometimes described as
OL,11,Fa "biological missile" or "Trojan
OL,12,Fhorse" therapy.
OL,14,FClinical trials have shown the drug,
OL,15,Fwhich is given by a drip once every
OL,16,Fthree weeks, can improve survival
OL,17,Famong patients by around four months
OL,18,Fon average, compared with those who
OL,19,Fhave chemotherapy alone.
OL,26,@sD@COUsD@VO]sD@[OUtD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/8
