PN,30505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780560334
OL,3,CFirst ovarian cancer treatment in two
OL,4,Cdecades approved for NHS use
OL,6,FNHS England said that 400 patients in
OL,7,FEngland each year could benefit.
OL,9,F"This represents the most significant
OL,10,Fbreakthrough in NHS treatment for
OL,11,Fthese hard-to-treat ovarian cancers in
OL,12,Fover two decades ` and we're delighted
OL,13,Fit will now offer hundreds of women
OL,14,Fmuch-needed hope of precious extra
OL,15,Ftime with their loved ones," said
OL,16,FProfessor Ruth Plummer, NHS England's
OL,17,Fnational clinical lead for cancer
OL,18,Fdrugs.
OL,26,@qD@AOUwD@\O]
