FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780560334
OL,3,CFirst ovarian cancer treatment in two
OL,4,Cdecades approved for NHS use
OL,6,FPatricia Hill, 64, a retired NHS
OL,7,Fphysiotherapist from north London, who
OL,8,Fbegan treatment in January this year,
OL,9,Fsaid: "Previously, I've had three
OL,10,Fdifferent lines of chemotherapy, and
OL,11,Fthis is the first time that I've
OL,12,Factually been able to get on with my
OL,13,Flife in terms of the impact of side
OL,14,Feffects.
OL,16,F"The feelings of isolation and
OL,17,Floneliness that you have undergoing
OL,18,Fconventional chemotherapy are totally
OL,19,For more or less totally eradicated
OL,20,Fwhen using mirvetuximab.
OL,26,@qD@GOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/8
