FL,306,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F305A1780560334
OL,3,CFirst ovarian cancer treatment in two
OL,4,Cdecades approved for NHS use
OL,6,F"It actually adds life to years,
OL,7,Frather than spending your life in bed
OL,8,Frecovering from the side effects of
OL,9,Fchemotherapy."
OL,11,FRachel Downing, head of policy and
OL,12,Fexternal affairs at Target Ovarian
OL,13,FCancer, said: "This is a hugely
OL,14,Fimportant moment for women with
OL,15,Fplatinum-resistant ovarian cancer and
OL,16,Ftheir families, who have faced limited
OL,17,Feffective treatment options for far
OL,18,Ftoo long. Today's announcement offers
OL,19,Freal hope of improved quality of life."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NO]uD@OOU
